description: Try our easy to follow Strawberries & Cream Finger Buns recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Strawberries & Cream Finger Buns Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: In a small bowl, swirl together strawberry jam and cream. Dollop onto the bottom of finger bun halves and top with strawberries. Replace top half of finger bun and serve immediately.
